data.description: Nestled on a quiet dead-end cul-du-sac and backing to the forest, this charming 2Story eludes timeless elegance and comfort. Step through the front door and be greeted by a 2 story entrance with an open-concept layout with open natural light to flood the living spaces, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. The living room features a bay window perfect for curling up with a good book on chilly evenings. Adjacent, the dining room boasts large windows that frame the lush forest backing to the property, providing a picturesque backdrop for gatherings. The heart of the home, the kitchen is a true masterpiece. Brand-new stainless steel appliances glisten under the recessed lighting., complementing the elegant quartz countertops and numerous custom cabinerty.  There is even a large pantry. Numerous cabinets and counters provides a focal point for culinary creativity and entertaining, The family room opens to the kitchen with a floor-to-ceiling fireplace and patio doors to the backyard. the bedrooms have been thoughtfully designed with comfort in mind. The master suite is a sanctuary unto itself, featuring a redesigned ensuite bathroom with sleek fixtures, a walk-in shower, and ample storage. All other bedrooms are generously sized.  The finished basement with 10 ft ceilings offer another living area. There is a kitchen area for entertaining, large rec room, a bath and bedroom area. This home is 2 zoned heating and ac.This home represents a harmonious blend of warmth and modern luxury. With its meticulously curated updates and attention to details, it offers a truly turnkey living experience.From the many updates to the stylish finishes, every element of this home has been thoughtfully considered,ensuring a living space that's functional as it is beautiful.
